data.description: Discover Unit 16 at 115 South St! Located in the Elms College area, this charming one-bedroom end unit awaits. Featuring a cozy living room with closet, an eat-in kitchen with a pantry and recessed lighting, plus a full bathroom with a linen closet. Relax on your private deck or venture into neighboring parks, coffee spots, and Chicopee Center amenities. Highway access from the Center expands the exciting possibilities. Seller states property is being sold as-is with recent updates including a water heater replacement in 2023. Shared coin-up laundry and utility room nearby. Unleash your imagination and transform this space into your personal haven today!
